outputs.output_descr: This activity encompassed the construction of an additional floor in the Tulkarem hospital as well as the rehabilitation of a number of departments in the old hospital.This is the third phase of the Construction of a new modern hospital in the Palestinian city of Tulkarem. The additional floor was contructed on top of two previously constructed floors. Services and the number of beds available for patients increased and improved.

project_descr: This is the third phase of the Construction of a new modern hospital in the Palestinian city of Tulkarem. An additional floor was contructed on top of two previously constructed floors and the original hospital was rehabilitated.
project_title: Construction of the Tulkarem Gov. Hospital - Phase III
